Update version number to 0.9, add entry for 'svn propedit', comment out

author: rooneg
msg: * subversion/clients/cmdline/main.c
(print_command_info): Only print the 'Valid options:' string if we actually
accept any options for this command.  Also, don't print the final newline
unless we had valid options, since without any options it just made the
output look weird.  While I'm here, clean out some trailing whitespace that
was annoying me.
